        </encoder>
    </appender>

    </root>

    <logger name="jclouds.wire">
        <level value="DEBUG" />
        <appender-ref ref="WIREFILE" />
    </logger>

    <logger name="jclouds.headers">
        <level value="DEBUG" />
        <appender-ref ref="WIREFILE" />
